            <script>
                var cur_sort = '';
                $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter a').on('click', function () {
                    var sort = $(this).data('sort');
                    if(sort === cur_sort) return;

                    if(sort === 'follow' && true){
                        window.location.href = '//www.douban.com/accounts/login?source=movie';
                        return;
                    }

                    if($('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').data('doing')) return;
                    $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').data('doing', true);

                    cur_sort = sort;

                    $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter a').removeClass('cur');
                    $(this).addClass('cur');

                    $.getJSON('reviews', { sort: sort }, function(res) {
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review-list').remove();
                        $('#reviews-wrapper [href="reviews?sort=follow"]').parent().remove();
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').after(res.html);
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').data('doing', false);
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').removeData('doing');

                        if (res.count === 0) {
                            $('#reviews-wrapper .review-list').html('<span class="no-review">你关注的人还没写过长评</span>');
                        }
                    });
                });
            </script>


            



<div class="review-list  ">
        
    

            
    
    <div data-cid="1147488">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1147488">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/linsinuo/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1250505-249.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/linsinuo/" class="name">都归尘土</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2007-04-22" class="main-meta">2007-04-22 00:02:25</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1147488/">穿过我的刀口你的寂寞</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1147488_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1147488">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        《三少爷的剑》在我喜欢的古龙小说里排名靠前，它是古龙小说一个比较特殊的文本，同时古龙在里面写尽他感兴趣的一切：荣耀，朋友，敌手，剑；女人，孩子，家庭；以及必不可少的贱民生活和英雄的重生，这些纠缠扭结的因素贯穿着故事主线，互相消解，又不断重生，这也可以看作古...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1147488-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1147488_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1147488_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1147488" title="有用">
